MaxVision Claude Marketplace — Licensing Overview

This repository is a multi-plugin Claude Code marketplace. Each plugin has
its own license file that governs the contents of that plugin's directory:

  - n8n-skills/LICENSE   (MIT — original work © Romuald Członkowski;
                                packaging © 2026 Produtora MaxVision)
